Description: Reimplementation of Tomb Raider 1 by LostArtefacts
 Released in 1996, Tomb Raider is a groundbreaking action-adventure game
 featuring Lara Croft, a fearless archaeologist on a quest for ancient and
 mysterious artifacts. Armed with her iconic dual pistols, she explores perilous
 tombs, solves complex puzzles, and faces deadly enemies, embarking on an
 adventure that has left a lasting mark on video game history.

